data.description:
Fabulous renovated and spacious 8 bedroom 4 full Bathroom home on corner lot. Rooms will be rented out individually and if this listing is live, there's still an opportunity for you to get in! There are currently 3 female tenants renting out 3 of the rooms separately. Rents in the house are $750+/month (utilities not included) depending on the size of the room and access to bathrooms.Remodeled gourmet kitchen with wood cabinets, granite counters, SS appliances and modern tile floors. Beautifully renovated bathrooms, recessed lighting and new fixtures throughout. Private spacious deck and backyard. There is a large off street driveway foe parking as well as a garage for rent (if interested, feel free to ask) lot of parking with a garaGreat Basement rooms are also available with eat-in kitchenette, living room dining combo. Wifi included!In the application, there will be:- credit check- verification of income- background checkRestrictions:- No cats- No dogs- No smoking

Smoking allowed:No
